tid":739900,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"可能多人報<br />\n學額有限(超收都唔可以太過分)"},{"pid":"f28dbe86ceb4e11002a3a71f348160494002fa54","tid":739900,"uid":137056,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"HKCC 放榜後的遴選共分多少輪?<br />\n7 月12 至15 日分四輪遴選（每一輪未獲取錄的申請人，自動進入下一輪）。<br />\n第一輪遴選公佈時間<br />\n&bull; 7 月12 日下午1 時後（放榜前的申請）<br />\n&bull; 7 月12 日下午2 時後（放榜後的申請）<br />\n第二、三、四輪公佈時間<br />\n&bull; 7 月13 至15 日每天下午2 時後（所有申請）<br />\n如何查閱取錄結果<br />\n依時登入HKCC 網上入學申請系統(OAA)：<a href=\"http://www.hkccpolyu.edu.hk/hkccoaa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkccpolyu.edu.hk%2Fhkccoaa&d=uJLkQzv8w54hPBWmsmKDI0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=bf761363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkccpolyu.edu.hk/hkccoaa</a> 查閱取錄結果。獲取錄者會收到SMS及電郵通知。<br />\n獲取錄後該做甚麼<br />\n獲取錄者須於翌日按電郵上指定時間親身前往理大紅磡灣校園領取「正式取錄通知書」。<br />\n若7 月15 日後仍未獲取錄<br />\n屆時如有剩餘學額，HKCC 將會考慮未獲取錄的申請人。"},{"pid":"45e43c148125874263a98d97dd5d222bd1c0cbe9","tid":739900,"uid":176780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61e63679dcb29f12e1214115bcf0bd1d6ae50b6c","tid":739900,"uid":105614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一咗咪要進一步甄選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"1咗就唔會報啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ef57b0d126a2b525de623ba39b2cdc65f572fb","tid":739900,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"無架啦, 趁早搵下ive收滿未啦 hkcc好易收滿"},{"pid":"115ab595b965c81c711825fc343248ea746c0fbe","tid":739900,"uid":139735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e9d236cf98dab62a6d8584b5ea4069d4531adc7","tid":739900,"uid":125663,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:26:46.000Z